title: Redeeming The Time | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Redeeming The Time | Joel Osteen
description:
Time is one of the most valuable commodities we have. When you see each day as the gift that is, you’ll recognize the responsibility you have to pursue your God-given purpose. You have everything you need to become who He created you to be.


Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
